# Workflows (how we build features)

## Adding items
- Add suggestions via URL ingestion (`/api/bachelor-party/add`).
- Auto-categorize activities; classify lodging; best-effort coordinates (site HTML → geocode fallback).
- Keep items lightweight: name + short definition + link + coordinates.

## Converging on an itinerary
- Use **Shortlist** as the “wide table” of candidates.
- Votes are **one per browser** (cookie-backed session id); sort by votes descending.
- Drag from shortlist into the day plan; keep day picker scoped per destination.

## Persistence rules
- Shared: compendium + shortlist + votes in `data/bachelor_party.json`.
- Local: per-user selections (active day, UI state) in localStorage.

## Deployment (Koyeb)
- Keep `Procfile` as source of truth for run command (Gunicorn + `$PORT`).
- Pin Python via `.python-version`.
- Revoke API tokens after deploy.
